text: Hello!  If the creature has orange or yellow wings, feathers or stripes, it is wudsy.
If it has green or purple wings, feathers or stripes, it is not.
I seem to have forgotten for blue, but I am pretty sure if it has blue wings, feathers or stripes, it is wudsy.
The body color does not matter.
Got it! Thanks for the info
Okay, best of luck.  Hopefully, I've remembered correctly, but I'm sure, we can deduce any mistakes as we go along.
